browserTools.browser_navigate: Navigate the browser to the specified URL.
browserTools.browser_go_back: Go back to the previous page in the current tab.
browserTools.browser_go_forward: Go forward to the next page in the current tab.
browserTools.browser_new_tab: Open a new browser tab (window) for the session.
browserTools.browser_tab_list: List all tabs (windows) for the current session.
browserTools.browser_switch_tab: Activate a specific tab (window) by its id.
browserTools.browser_close_tab: Close a tab (window). Defaults to the active tab.
browserTools.browser_get_text: Extract visible text from the page or a specific element.
browserTools.browser_get_markdown: Extract the page content as Markdown.
browserTools.browser_read_links: List hyperlinks on the current page.
browserTools.browser_get_clickable_elements: List clickable elements with simple selectors.
browserTools.browser_click: Click an element on the page using a CSS selector.
browserTools.browser_hover: Hover over an element on the page.
browserTools.browser_form_input_fill: Fill text into an input or textarea element.
browserTools.browser_select: Select value(s) within a select element.
browserTools.browser_scroll: Scroll the page by specified offsets.
browserTools.browser_press_key: Send keyboard input to the active page.
browserTools.browser_screenshot: Capture a screenshot of the current page or a specific element.
browserTools.browser_get_download_list: Get download items for the current browser session.
browserTools.browser_download_file: Download a file using the browser session, preserving cookies of the active tab.
